description.text: Welcome to 56 Fane Court! This charming & well-maintained one-family home in Gerritsen Beach is very affordable and has so much to offer! On the first floor you have a big entry foyer with closet, living room, dining room and an updated eat-in kitchen with granite countertops. The first floor also offers an updated full bath & laundry room. On the second floor you have 3 bedrooms plus an additional modern bathroom with a big stall shower! The entire home is bright & airy with lots of windows, new wall-to-wall carpet, 5 closets and a modern wall mounted tankless boiler & hot water heater! This property also features a private backyard & large storage shed in the back as well! The location provides access to a plethora of outdoor activities, parks, Kiddie Beach, schools, shopping & eats! Short walk to B31 & BM4 bus to Manhattan. Why rent when you can own a home? Do not miss the opportunity to make this your dream home.... Schedule a showing today!
